       true,
       "inspect.isfunction.__class__.__name__.__eq__('function') == True — isfunction is a Python function defined in Lib/inspect.py; __class__.__name__ is 'function'; str.__eq__('function') returns True; new to extra140"]
    - [isfunction_doc_class_eq_str,
