       ["isfunction"],
       true,
       "inspect.isfunction.__qualname__.__eq__('isfunction') == True — the function's __qualname__ is 'isfunction'; str.__eq__('isfunction') returns True; new to extra140"]
    - [isfunction_qualname_len_eq_10,
